{{Weapon}}

== Overview ==
A powerful coupling of four standard [[Argon Laser|Argon Lasers]] merged into a singular slot bracing. The resulting projectile from this weapon has the power of four argon lasers all in one shot.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Baron Laser can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
